30 pages. Various minor errors corrected, results unchanged;
  statement of some propositions and proofs improved; sketch of full system of
  Principia added

18 pages, 15 figures, accepted for publication in A&A;
  high-resolution PDF version available also at
  http://www.mpifr.de/staff/jgroh/etacar.html

Invited talk at the EPS-HEPP meeting in Krakow, July 2009. To be
  published in the Proceedings. v. 2 Serious error in last section corrected;
  minor stylistic changes.
